{"tid":2346802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑暗中心懷希望，堅守到黎明] 英藉官員被俘虜仍然冒死製作文宣","createTime":"2020-12-30T13:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T10:51:31.000Z","uid":43150,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c662e4f42e60099a773e1077e28efc3bb0d013","tid":2346802,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/%e3%80%90%e6%98%8e%e5%a4%b7%e5%be%85%e8%a8%aa%ef%bc%8c%e7%ad%89%e5%be%85%e9%87%8d%e5%85%89%e3%80%911944%e5%b9%b4%e7%89%88%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%87%8d%e5%85%89%e9%83%b5%e7%a5%a8%ef%bc%9f/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%25a4%25b7%25e5%25be%2585%25e8%25a8%25aa%25ef%25bc%258c%25e7%25ad%2589%25e5%25be%2585%25e9%2587%258d%25e5%2585%2589%25e3%2580%25911944%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e7%2589%2588%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2587%258d%25e5%2585%2589%25e9%2583%25b5%25e7%25a5%25a8%25ef%25bc%259f%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=24c1840f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.watershedhk.com/%e3%80%90%e6%98%8e%e5%a4%b7%e5%be%85%e8%a8%aa%ef%bc%8c%e7%ad%89%e5%be%85%e9%87%8d%e5%85%89%e3%80%911944%e5%b9%b4%e7%89%88%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%87%8d%e5%85%89%e9%83%b5%e7%a5%a8%ef%bc%9f/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Picture-2-830x500.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2FPicture-2-830x500.png&h=9c27e8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1941年香港淪陷後，原港府官員都被日軍囚禁在戰俘營，條件非常惡劣。但這些英國人，在黑暗歲月仍時刻在準備光復的一天。<br />\n<br />\n其中囚於赤柱的工務局高級繪圖主任鍾惠霖（William Jones） 與郵政署長榮鍾思（Edward Wynne-Jones）兩人秘密設計香港重光郵票，甚至要放線眼避開日軍監察。這張郵票初稿上的年份，原先寫上1941-1944。因為那個時候，他們仍不知道哪一年香港才會重光。可以想像，他們在戰俘營中，周遭何其黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n不過，他們眼中有重光的盼望。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>郵票的正中央，英王之下，有一隻浴火鳳凰，象徵香港歷盡劫難後，終有重光之日。</strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，他們等到了，這個設計成為了香港重光一周年紀念郵票。<br />\n<br />\n其他英國官員也在這段黑暗的日子中，構思戰後收回香港，如何重建。他們在淪陷劫難中的經歷，亦促成了戰後一系列改革。其中最為人熟知的，也許是曾服役於香港義勇防衛軍的鄔勵德，受到戰俘營經歷影響，戰後在工務局提倡每個房協屋邨單位都應有獨立的廁所和廚房，改善港人生活水準。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>除了盼望，還要堅持意志，做好準備。你我共勉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n鄺智文：《重光之路：日據香港與太平洋戰爭》。香港：天地圖書，2015。頁410－412。<br />\n<br />\n吳貴龍：〈勝利和平紀念郵票〉，取自：<a href=\"http://www.cpa-hk.net/chin1/HK%20&rsquo;STUDY/VICTORY/victory.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpa-hk.net%2Fchin1%2FHK%2520%E2%80%99STUDY%2FVICTORY%2Fvictory.htm&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=4e376286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cpa-hk.net/chin1/HK%20&rsquo;STUDY/VICTORY/victory.htm</a>"},{"pid":"18f9420a17040da6fc95e38852e45a135427d196","tid":2346802,"uid":43150,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"最後出品  (source: Wikipedia) <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9d/Timbre_HK_Victory_1D_1946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F9%2F9d%2FTimbre_HK_Victory_1D_1946.jpg&h=4666e334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"087c0093c5991c492c6825638ee0b04a964c15ab","tid":2346802,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f83632fcf308133f0378febbb41852434b2e5ca","tid":2346802,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211ca53f9ffd60bdc812f4899ae5de856f0b5138","tid":2346802,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1e7eafb0d47cfddcdceb80415b599d84eee230","tid":2346802,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,